data.description: Curb Appeal! This stunning Waters Edge home catches the eye of anyone passing by! Bringing Colonial architecture to this already breathtaking Gated Community, this home welcomes you with a large front porch, and a balcony from the 2nd floor that creates a seasonal view of the 9 acre Waters Edge Lake. This home also boasts nearly 2,500 sqft of living space, 2 living rooms, a designated office, and 3, could be 4 large bedrooms! Updated from the floor to ceiling, the present owners have poured their love into this home to bring you amazing updates that blend this older architecture beautifully into 2023! Updates include: New plank flooring in the main living spaces, including the stairs and upstairs hallway! New Carpet in all the bedrooms, and updated kitchen with granite countertops, a unique chevron tiled fireplace, and new paint throughout! Don't forget about the 3 car garage and the large fenced backyard! Call today to schedule your private tour!
